Steps to perform
	1. curl -fLo ~/.vim/autoload/plug.vim --create-dirs \
    		https://raw.githubusercontent.com/junegunn/vim-plug/master/plug.vim
	2. Open vim and do :PlugInstall
	3. do 
		a. yay -S nodejs yarn ripgrep
		b. cd ~/.vim/plugged/coc.nvim(Vim) or ~/.config/coc/
		c. yarn install
		d. install language engine you want for CoC with command
		in vim
			:CocInstall <language engine>
